title: Shuyan Saga-PLAZA
description:
Shuyan Saga (c) Lofty Sky Entertainment Inc

Release Date: 08/2017 Protection: Discs: 1 Genre: Action

Shuyan Saga is a graphic novel series where action scenes come alive
through 3D combat gameplay. Set in an ancient Chinese martial arts
fantasy universe, the player embarks on a life-changing journey as
Shuyan a carefree Princess fed-up with her constricted and pampered
life to become a true disciple of Kung-Fu and stop the evil Guer
horde from destroying the Five Kingdoms

For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/594680/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Play!
